reviewText: I would have to say that my favorite scene does not include Kayden.  There is a girl/girl/girl scene with three great natural girls and at the end of the scene there is some nice dildo play.  Kayden is in the introductory scene and two others and is her usual perky self.  The first scene with Kayden is very good because she does a nice solo strip scene before walking down the grassy hill to meet her lover who is enjoying a warm day soon to become quite hot.  The final scene is with a pretty brunette who takes on two guys.  Some of the girls are all natural and one or two not, but all are pretty.  Not perfect, buy very good movie.
